<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 01:15:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在冲突中比特币徘徊在交易区间下限附近</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</link><description>由于中东冲突的影响持续存在不确定性，比特币交易价格接近其一个多月交易区间的下限。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iemMEm5XlsqQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 04:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/bitcoin-tumbles-with-stocks-as-trump-signals-harder-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>窃取中本聪的比特币成为量子计算的威胁</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-02/stealing-satoshi-s-bitcoin-becomes-a-quantum-computing-threat</link><description>谷歌研究论文引发担忧&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itU5Gc2d.COg/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-02/stealing-satoshi-s-bitcoin-becomes-a-quantum-computing-threat</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 表示其信托宪章已获得美国有条件批准</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-says-it-wins-conditional-us-approval-for-trust-charter</link><description>美国最大的加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 表示，其国家信托公司执照已获得银行监管机构有条件批准，此举可能为其拓展新业务铺平道路。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieCY.f6h1US8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 15:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-says-it-wins-conditional-us-approval-for-trust-charter</guid></item><item><title>比特币“鲸鱼”抛售削弱了机构需求</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</link><description>尽管机构购买有所增加，但比特币需求仍然面临压力，这表明更广泛的市场仍在抛售该代币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iuZpxHDg1q1s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 22:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-buying-fails-to-offset-a-wave-of-selling-by-big-holders</guid></item><item><title>价值 2.8 亿美元的加密货币黑客事件暴露了 DeFi 中的人为薄弱环节</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</link><description>Drift 是一个基于 Solana 区块链的去中心化金融项目，遭到黑客攻击，该协议损失了近 3 亿美元的数字资产，使其成为加密货币历史上最大的漏洞之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioQmeBKVq_zE/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:25:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/solana-based-defi-project-drift-hit-by-285-million-exploit</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase、Cloudflare、Stripe 推动塑造人工智能货币的未来</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-cloudflare-stripe-push-to-shape-future-of-ai-money</link><description>加密货币、支付和云基础设施领域的知名人士正在竞相为人工智能代理（而不是人类）处理互联网交易的世界构建金融管道。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihyFcJs4ngz4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-02/coinbase-cloudflare-stripe-push-to-shape-future-of-ai-money</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 解决了针对前 FTX 工程主管 Singh 的案件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/cftc-resolves-fraud-case-against-ex-ftx-engineering-chief-singh</link><description>根据与美国衍生品监管机构就其在倒闭的加密货币交易所中所扮演角色达成的和解协议，前 FTX 工程主管尼沙德·辛格 (Nishad Singh) 必须返还 370 万美元的非法利润。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioAh7.q6.eug/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 19:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/cftc-resolves-fraud-case-against-ex-ftx-engineering-chief-singh</guid></item><item><title>比特币支持的市政债券扫清了穆迪评级的障碍</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</link><description>风险最高的资产类别正在与同类中最安全的金融产品之一融合：比特币支持的市政债券。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i53JkSgE1_dA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Mar 2026 18:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-31/bitcoin-backed-municipal-bond-clears-hurdle-with-moody-s-rating</guid></item><item><title>比特币在连续五个月下跌结束后保持小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-holds-gains-in-asia-after-five-month-losing-streak-ends</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普打算在几周内结束对伊朗的战争的推动下，比特币在结束了 3 月份连续五个月的下跌后，周三保持微幅上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ijL7KT0RVqno/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 01:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/bitcoin-holds-gains-in-asia-after-five-month-losing-streak-ends</guid></item><item><title>Zodia Markets 首席执行官艾哈迈德离开渣打银行支持的加密货币公司</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/zodia-markets-ceo-ahmad-departs-stanchart-backed-crypto-firm</link><description>知情人士称，渣打银行旗下加密货币交易子公司 Zodia Markets Holdings Ltd. 的首席执行官已离开该公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.hAwjimIt1I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 09:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/zodia-markets-ceo-ahmad-departs-stanchart-backed-crypto-firm</guid></item><item><title>“区块链岛”因加密货币监管而与欧盟对抗</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/malta-fights-back-against-eu-s-crypto-regulation-plans</link><description>欧洲的金融监管之战通常是通过外交手段进行的。这里是一个措辞简洁的声明，那里是一个隐晦的信号。但在拥有黄金签证、大麻合法化和庞大赌博业的马耳他小岛上，参与规则却有所不同。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM0dsIlGR7XA/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/malta-fights-back-against-eu-s-crypto-regulation-plans</guid></item></channel></rss>